# Variáveis de Ambiente - Mini ERP Juds

## Backend (NestJS/API)
NODE_ENV=production
DATABASE_URL=postgres://user:password@host:port/database?schema=public&sslmode=require
REDIS_URL=redis://default:password@host:port
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-change-in-production
JWT_EXPIRATION=24h
PORT=3000

## Frontend (Angular)
API_URL=https://your-domain.com/api
ENVIRONMENT=production

## Desenvolvimento Local
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://erp_juds:erp_juds_2024@localhost:5432/erp_juds?schema=public
# REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

## Serviços Recomendados para Produção
# Banco de Dados: Supabase, Neon, AWS RDS, ou Railway
# Redis: Redis Cloud, AWS ElastiCache, ou Railway
# Backend: Vercel, Railway, Render
# Frontend: Vercel, Netlify, GitHub Pages
